issue.title: Emoji picker: certain flag selection results in different flag
issue.body:
**To Reproduce**

Steps to reproduce the behaviour:
1. Go to any document
2. Open emoji picker
3. Type :singa for singapore, select it, get the wrong flag.

**Expected behaviour**

When clicking an emoji flag, I expect the same flag to be inserted into the document.

**Videos**

Video shows it well.

Note how it's not all flags! But certain ones seem to trigger it like Singapore.

https://github.com/outline/outline/assets/88744/f9cee7b0-09aa-470a-a62c-92a57d1c29fb

**Outline (please complete the following information):**
- Install: getoutline.com (26 Oct 18:19 BST)

**Desktop (please complete the following information):**
 - OS: MacOS Ventura 13.5.1
 - Browser: Arc
 - Version: 1.12.1
